userTemplate:
Language preference: {{lang}}
Brand: {{brand}}
Goal: {{goal}}
Target audience: {{targetAudience}}
Link: {{link}}

Create a mission plan with:
- mission_title, objective
- steps (3-10 actionable steps)
- proof (proofType: SIGN_MESSAGE/SCREENSHOT/LINK/TEXT, instructions, submissionFormat)
- reward_structure: top_reward, participation_reward, scoring(action+points), budgetCap(currency,maxParticipants,maxTotalReward)
- ranking_model (how winners determined)
- anti_sybil_mechanism (simple but real)
- growth: viralCoefficientEstimate (rough), shareHooks, referralLoop
- economics: costDrivers, expectedROI, sustainabilityNotes
- risk: abuseVectors, mitigations, edgeCases
- recommendedCopy: tweet_zh, tweet_en, hashtags(3-6), cta (if link provided, include it; otherwise no URL)

Return ONLY JSON exactly matching:
{
  "mission_title":"...",
  "objective":"...",
  "steps":["..."],
  "proof":{"proofType":"SIGN_MESSAGE","proofInstructions":"...","submissionFormat":"..."},
  "reward_structure":{
    "top_reward":"...",
    "participation_reward":"...",
    "scoring":[{"action":"...","points":10}],
    "budgetCap":{"currency":"USD","maxParticipants":500,"maxTotalReward":1000}
  },
  "ranking_model":"...",
  "anti_sybil_mechanism":"...",
  "growth":{"viralCoefficientEstimate":1.2,"shareHooks":["..."],"referralLoop":"..."},
  "economics":{"costDrivers":["..."],"expectedROI":"...","sustainabilityNotes":"..."},
  "risk":{"abuseVectors":["..."],"mitigations":["..."],"edgeCases":["..."]},
  "recommendedCopy":{"tweet_zh":"...","tweet_en":"...","hashtags":["#WAOC"],"cta":"..."}
}

If lang is "zh", write mission_title/objective/steps/proof/reward/growth/economics/risk in Simplified Chinese, but recommendedCopy must include BOTH tweet_zh and tweet_en.
